' @id(SEQ-OPEN-RENDER)
' @ref(USE-OPEN-RENDER)
'
' Objective-side flow for the contextual "Open render" button on the
' central-panel view-tab row. Enabled only when the selected model file is a
' mockup whose slug has a React render (mockups/src/mockups/<slug>.tsx).
' Start-if-needed: probe :4317 and spawn `npm run dev` in mockups/ only when
' the port is not already serving, then open the OS browser at the route.
'
' @desc(SEQ-OPEN-RENDER, "Clicking the contextual 'Open render' button launches the selected mockup's React render: the launcher derives the route /mockup/<slug>, probes localhost:4317, spawns `npm run dev` in the repo-root mockups/ dir only if the port is not already serving, then opens the OS default browser at the route. The button is enabled only when mockups/src/mockups/<slug>.tsx exists.")
title Open the React render of the selected mockup (objective)

actor "Developer" as Dev <<missing>>
participant "MddViewer\n(view-tab row)" as Viewer
participant "MockupLauncher\n(CMP-MOCKUP-LAUNCH)" as Launch
boundary "TCP localhost:4317" as Port
participant "npm run dev\n(Vite, cwd mockups/)" as Vite
control "OS default browser" as Browser

Dev -> Viewer : select a mockup .puml in the rail
alt slug has a render (mockups/src/mockups/<slug>.tsx exists)
  Viewer --> Dev : enabled "Open render" button (UIC-OPEN-RENDER)
else no render for this slug
  Viewer --> Dev : button disabled
end

Dev -> Viewer : click "Open render"
Viewer -> Launch : open_render(slug)
Launch -> Port : connect probe :4317
alt already serving
  Port --> Launch : reachable — reuse
else not reachable
  Launch -> Vite : spawn `npm run dev` (cwd = mockups/)
  Vite --> Launch : serving on :4317
end
Launch -> Browser : open http://localhost:4317/mockup/<slug>
Browser --> Dev : React render of the mockup
@enduml
